paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, east, south, southwest, northwest
description: The maze created by the tunnels would be the envy of any minotaur.  Branches wind off to nearly all compass directions, spinning through the dirt like the work of a drunken roa'ter.  A single lantern dangles from the wooden planks above, shedding a sickly light over the area.
title: [Smuggling Tunnels, Passage]
